Machine check interrupt
External interrupt
I/O interrupt


Interrupt operation sequence
1. IRQ interrupt request
2. wait current program
3. saving current program counter(PC)
4. interrut handling routine
5. ISR interrupt service routine
6. recervey PC
7. resuming interrupted program execution

Interrupt priority sequence 
Power fail > Machine Check > External > I/O > Commend Error > Program Check > SuperVisor Call

memory manager in Mainboard 
user => kernel : context switching

Direct X high performance interface 
